description:
To make the WBFS into a ISO file you need a program called &quot;Wii Backup Manager&quot;

(You can find &quot;Wii Backup Manager&quot; in my uploaded Torrents so if you need it you can download it there)

Step 1:Extract WBM with Winrar or 7-Zip
Step 2:Open WBM and select &quot;Add&quot; and then &quot;files..&quot;
Step 3:Select the WBFS file that came in the Torrent
Step 4:Click the checkbox then click &quot;Transfer&quot; then &quot;ISO..&quot;
Step 5:Burn the ISO to a disc or use &quot;WBFS Manager&quot; to put it on a flashdrive

I hope this tutorial helped comment if you have any trouble I will be glad to help
